jalse.attributes

Class DefaultAttributeContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • jalse.attributes.DefaultAttributeContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeContainer

    public class DefaultAttributeContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements AttributeContainer
    An DefaultAttributeContainer is a thread-safe implementation of AttributeContainer.

    DefaultAttributeContainer can take a delegate AttributeContainer to supply to AttributeEvent. Attribute updates will trigger these events using AttributeListener.
